posting_body: ['Welcome to Prism', 'A Prism of Possibility.', 'The Mid-Market neighborhood is a treasure trove of hidden gems — social, cultural and culinary.', 'It’s a vibrant spectrum of restaurants, cafés, theater, nightlife, shops, museums, plazas and parklets.', 'This is the new Mid-Market… a renaissance in action.', 'The official Walk Score rates Mid-Market a “walking, transit and biking paradise.”', 'Many of San Francisco’s largest employers are within a 15-minute walk or 8-minute bike ride.', 'By foot, bike, train, bus, subway, cable car.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Glass-enclosed Conference Room', 'Grill and Kitchen', 'Lounge Seating', 'Resident Storage Lockers', 'Picnic Lawn', 'Pet Friendly Community', 'Mobile-enabled Smart Locks', 'Attended Lobby / Lounge Area', 'City Views / Bay Views', 'Dining Area', 'Fitness Center with Peloton Bikes', 'Secure Bicycle Storage', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
